(2.2 The Vault is the Disk) show newline
(-------------------------) show newline
() show newline
(VAXcluster had multiple subsystems \(MSCP, DLM, SCS, quorum disk, LAVC\).) show newline
(Cyberspace has one abstraction: the vault. It subsumes all of them.) show newline
() show newline
